      "content": "Please do not stop your prescribed warfarin or make changes to your diet without consulting your doctor. While green smoothies and garlic have some health benefits, they are not a substitute for your prescribed medication. Warfarin requires careful monitoring because it interacts with many things, and abruptly stopping it can be dangerous. Keep up with your scheduled tests to ensure your blood clotting remains within a safe range.",
      "source": "target",
